---
title: Crispy Chicken Milanese with Warm Potato-Scallion Salad & Green Beans
description: What’s for dinner? Milanese, please! This surprisingly simple cooking method calls for coating thin pieces of meat (chicken, in this case) in Italian-seasoned breadcrumbs, then frying until tender and golden. A tangy potato salad makes a hearty side, while a homemade garlic aioli stars in a creamy drizzle over chicken and steamed green beans. Weekend-worthy, while still weeknight-friendly, you’ll whip this meal up with Milan-ease!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/crispy-chicken-milanese-1b7a119b.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/crispy-chicken-milanese-6231e96c5bad8a79494a99e1-b5df25f9.pdf
time required: 35 minutes
